The paper introduces a visual SLAM framework that is essential for AR devices, autonomous control of robots and drones, etc. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-categories. The paper also mentions that the software incorporates several useful features and functions for research and development, which suggests that it may also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper mentions that the software is designed to be easily used and extended, which suggests that it may also belong to the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
